To improve the Daily Dispatch's news coverage of Buffalo City Metro, our City news desk is focusing on each of the metro's 50 wards. Every Tuesday on our special focus City News page we target one ward and highlight issues that relate directly to residents of this ward.If there are issues you would like us to investigate or highlight in your ward please get in touch by using our email address: city@dispatch.co.za or call 043 702 2000 or WhatsApp us on 062 578 3098.Of course we also love to spread good news, so let us know this about your ward too.